The '''14th Infantry Brigade''' was a [[formation (military)|formation]] of the [[Royal Hungarian Army]] that participated in the [[Axis powers|Axis]] [[invasion of Yugoslavia]] during [[World War II]].{{sfn|Thomas|Szabo|2008|p=14}}

