===BBC Two=== Scotland has regional programming such as ''[[Newsnight Scotland]]'' and [[Scottish Gaelic language|Gaelic-language]] programmes. Northern Ireland and Wales also have regional programming, but on digital TV there is only a single BBC Two service for England.
