[[File:Odznaka-zasluzony-dla-kultury-polskiej-PL.jpg|right|thumb|362x362px|Meritorious for Polish Culture]] The '''Decoration of Honor Meritorious for Polish Culture''' ({{lang-pl|Odznaka Honorowa "Zasłużony dla Kultury Polskiej"}}) or '''Meritorious for Polish Culture''', is a [[Polish departmental decoration ]]in Arts awarded by the [[Ministry of Culture and National Heritage of the Republic of Poland]] to persons and organizations for distinguished contributions to the Polish culture and heritage. This award was instituted on 11 August 1969.<ref>http://www.mkidn.gov.pl/media/docs/2012/20120203_rozp_ZKP.pdf</ref>
